summary: This is an email chain from October 23, 2020, regarding the completion of a forensic examination of a final drive. It involves FBI personnel and a NY CART Coordinator/Senior Forensic Examiner discussing where to deliver the completed drive. The document is subject to a protective order.

keyFacts: A forensic examination of a 'final drive' was completed on or before October 23, 2020.
FBI personnel were coordinating the physical transfer of this completed drive to a NY CART Coordinator/Senior Forensic Examiner.
The document is explicitly marked as 'SUBJECT TO PROTECTIVE ORDER' covering specific paragraphs, indicating restricted access.
The document references case identifiers EFTA_00002277 and EFTA00157450.
